<div style="font-family: 'Bitstream Vera Sans', arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; color: #203070; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 17px;">
    <blockquote>
        <br />
        <h3>Your subscription has been activated!</h3>
        <br />
        Congratulation! Your subscription has been successfully activated. You are now subscribed for email updates.
        <br /><br />
        Welcome on board!
        <br />

        <h3>Requested By</h3>
        <blockquote>
            <table>
                <tr valign="top">
                    <td>IP</td>
                    <td width="32" style="text-align:center;">-</td>
                    <td>
                        <span style="color: #900; font-weight: normal;">
                            ${client-ip}
                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>

                <tr valign="top">
                    <td>Location</td>
                    <td width="32" style="text-align:center;">-</td>
                    <td>
                        <span style="color: #900; font-weight: normal;">
